These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: gospel, trance, reggae, r&b, folk, metal, pop
1. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of trance##1
2. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
3. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
4. the fan of folk is between the fan of gospel and the fan of reggae##2
5. the fan of r&b is between the fan of trance and the fan of gospel##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Music-Genre   | pop | reggae | folk | gospel | r&b | trance | metal |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: traveling, dancing, writing, gardening, singing, board-games, photography
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
6. the person who's hobby is writing is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Hobby   | board-games | photography | traveling | writing | gardening | dancing | singing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: rock-climbing, singing, writing, chess, collecting, drawing, puzzles
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's hobby is singing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Hobby   | puzzles | drawing | collecting | singing | rock-climbing | writing | chess |

